sentences.english: Skip ran abreast of him toward the river.
sentences.chinese: 斯基普和他并肩朝河边跑去。

sentences.english: A year into his sentence, Kyp's parents were killed in a prison revolt.
sentences.chinese: 服刑一年后，基普的父母死于一次监狱暴动。

sentences.english: Skip jumped feet-first, his plunge almost at the same time with Daniel's.
sentences.chinese: 斯基普几乎和丹尼尔同时跳入水中。

sentences.english: Kyprioanou asked Hu to convey his cordial greetings to Chairman Li Peng.
sentences.chinese: 基普里亚努请胡锦涛转达对李鹏委员长的亲切问候。

sentences.english: Kyp would become one of the founding members of this new governing body of the Jedi order.
sentences.chinese: 基普将成为这个绝地武士团新管理机构的创始人之一。

sentences.english: Brian has sex with his co-worker, Kip, in Brian's office.
sentences.chinese: 布莱恩在办公室跟同事基普发生性关系。

sentences.english: The years of hardship had tainted Kyp, though.
sentences.chinese: 不过，多年的艰辛生活扭曲了基普的心理。

sentences.english: SKINNER, still carrying GIBSON PRAISE, enters the emergency area of the hospital.
sentences.chinese: 斯金纳，还在抱着基普森普雷兹，进入医院急诊区。

sentences.english: Filled with righteous vengeance, Kyp sought to end the Empire's destructive ways.
sentences.chinese: 基普满怀正义的复仇感，寻求终结帝国毁灭性的行径。
